,imgsize-53652.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US charges tech CEO over alleged exports of restricted equipment to Iran]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131495080.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-charges-tech-ceo-over-alleged-exports-of-restricted-equipment-to-iran/articleshow/131495080.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-charges-tech-ceo-over-alleged-exports-of-restricted-equipment-to-iran/articleshow/131495080.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T08:11:53+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131495140,imgsize-50716.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Lack of effort' to free Imran Khan? Pakistan Tehreek-i-Insaf lawmakers revolt against party leadership]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131495048.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A significant internal rift has emerged within PTI in Khyber Pakhtunkhwa as lawmakers express dissatisfaction with the party leadership's efforts to secure Imran Khan's release. Disgruntled MPAs, reportedly denied cabinet positions, have penned a letter to the PTI chairman, arguing the release campaign has lost momentum and become ineffective.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/lack-of-effort-to-free-imran-khan-pakistan-tehreek-i-insaf-lawmakers-revolt-against-party-leadership/articleshow/131495048.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/lack-of-effort-to-free-imran-khan-pakistan-tehreek-i-insaf-lawmakers-revolt-against-party-leadership/articleshow/131495048.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T08:09:59+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131495088,imgsize-544133.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Trump says US, Iran to jointly remove buried nuclear material; Tehran sees no breakthrough in talks]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131495261.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-says-us-iran-to-jointly-remove-buried-nuclear-material-tehran-sees-no-breakthrough-in-talks/articleshow/131495261.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-says-us-iran-to-jointly-remove-buried-nuclear-material-tehran-sees-no-breakthrough-in-talks/articleshow/131495261.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T08:34:24+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131495588,imgsize-50904.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["I was so scared": Pokimane's nightmare birthday trip began with a medical emergency doctors rarely see]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131494309.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Twitch star Pokimane revealed she nearly suffered a serious eye injury before her 30th birthday trip to Paris. After experiencing severe pain and irritation, an emergency optometrist discovered an eyelash lodged inside a tear duct, a condition the doctor reportedly had never seen before. The eyelash was removed successfully, allowing Pokimane to travel. Her France trip later faced additional challenges, including accommodation issues and refund disputes.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/i-was-so-scared-pokimanes-nightmare-birthday-trip-began-with-a-medical-emergency-doctors-rarely-see/articleshow/131494309.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/i-was-so-scared-pokimanes-nightmare-birthday-trip-began-with-a-medical-emergency-doctors-rarely-see/articleshow/131494309.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T05:31:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131494309,imgsize-18926.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[New details surface as ChudTheBuilder’s release bid stalls despite Alex Rosen offering $100,000 toward bond]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131494307.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Dalton Eatherly, known as ChudTheBuilder, remains jailed after a Tennessee judge refused to lower his $1 million bond. YouTuber Alex Rosen offered $100,000 toward the bond, but Judge William Goodman III kept existing restrictions. Eatherly also faces separate charges in Nashville. The main case stems from a May 13 courthouse shooting involving Joshua Fox in Clarksville.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/new-details-surface-as-chudthebuilders-release-bid-stalls-despite-alex-rosen-offering-100000-toward-bond/articleshow/131494307.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/new-details-surface-as-chudthebuilders-release-bid-stalls-despite-alex-rosen-offering-100000-toward-bond/articleshow/131494307.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T05:10:49+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131494303,imgsize-677623.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[“Bro in a wheelchair?”: Clavicular’s new rhinoplasty recovery photos spark leg lengthening surgery speculation]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131494192.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Clavicular’s post-surgery photos have become a major talking point online. While the images clearly show him recovering from rhinoplasty, the leg braces and wheelchair seen in one photo led to widespread speculation about possible additional procedures. So far, no confirmed information has been released about any surgery other than the rhinoplasty, leaving many questions unanswered.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/bro-in-a-wheelchair-claviculars-new-rhinoplasty-recovery-photos-spark-leg-lengthening-surgery-speculation/articleshow/131494192.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/bro-in-a-wheelchair-claviculars-new-rhinoplasty-recovery-photos-spark-leg-lengthening-surgery-speculation/articleshow/131494192.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T04:20:10+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131494191,imgsize-2417937.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Who is Hasan Piker’s mom Ülker Sedef? Report links her to streamer’s college transfer after low GPA]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131492710.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Hasan Piker’s mother, Ülker Sedef Piker, is an art and architectural historian with degrees from Rutgers University and the New Jersey Institute of Technology. A recent New York Post report claimed Hasan transferred from the University of Miami to Rutgers after earning a 2.9 GPA. Hasan has often praised his mother, calling her a major source of inspiration.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/who-is-hasan-pikers-mom-lker-sedef-report-links-her-to-streamers-college-transfer-after-low-gpa/articleshow/131492710.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/who-is-hasan-pikers-mom-lker-sedef-report-links-her-to-streamers-college-transfer-after-low-gpa/articleshow/131492710.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T03:36:56+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131492572,imgsize-949704.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Techie living in $35 million mansion arrested for supplying sensitive US equipment to Iran]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131492050.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/california-techie-living-in-35-million-mansion-arrested-for-supplying-sensitive-us-equipment-to-irans-military-faces-up-to-20-years/articleshow/131492050.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/california-techie-living-in-35-million-mansion-arrested-for-supplying-sensitive-us-equipment-to-irans-military-faces-up-to-20-years/articleshow/131492050.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T02:23:10+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131492072,imgsize-162702.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[IShowSpeed’s viral ‘Champions’ song officially added to FIFA World Cup 2026 album]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131492012.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[IShowSpeed's song "Champions" has been officially added to the FIFA World Cup 2026 Official Album, a significant achievement following weeks of fan support. The track, released on May 31, quickly went viral, earning praise for its energetic sound and tribute to all 48 participating nations. This inclusion marks a major career milestone for the popular streamer and YouTuber.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/ishowspeeds-viral-champions-song-officially-added-to-fifa-world-cup-2026-album/articleshow/131492012.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/ishowspeeds-viral-champions-song-officially-added-to-fifa-world-cup-2026-album/articleshow/131492012.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T01:45:11+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131492011,imgsize-769426.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian national charged in crash that killed teen, victim’s mother calls for deportation]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131490617.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/mother-of-pregnant-teen-killed-in-ohio-crash-wants-33-year-old-indian-man-deported/articleshow/131490617.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/mother-of-pregnant-teen-killed-in-ohio-crash-wants-33-year-old-indian-man-deported/articleshow/131490617.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T01:12:40+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131491888,imgsize-96538.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Princess Diana's forgotten letter reveals what she wanted for Prince William and Prince Harry's future]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hs